{"id":5340,"date":"2012-08-18T21:11:26","date_gmt":"2012-08-19T01:11:26","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=5340"},"modified":"2023-04-17T17:16:41","modified_gmt":"2023-04-17T13:16:41","slug":"gracious-patience-first-strike","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/gracious-patience-first-strike\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sabr: Beautiful patience is at the first strike"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a woman who was weeping next to a grave. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Be mindful of<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>Allah and be patient<\/strong>.\u201d She said, \u201cGo away from me! You have not been afflicted by a calamity like mine,\u201d and she did not recognize him. Then, she was told that it was the Prophet, so she went to the\u00a0Prophet&#8217;s house and she did not find any guards there. She said to him, \u201cI did not recognize you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Verily, patience is at the first strike<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1283, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 926<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/i><\/b>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0629\u064d \u062a\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0643\u0650\u064a \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064d